295
00:24:36,224 --> 00:24:37,254
Je teplo?

296
00:24:46,924 --> 00:24:48,554
Čo? Som škaredá?

297
00:24:48,924 --> 00:24:50,654
Čo? Akože škaredá?

298
00:24:52,494 --> 00:24:53,624
Čia si dcéra?

299
00:24:54,224 --> 00:24:55,224
Tvoja.

300
00:24:55,225 --> 00:24:56,993
Presne tak. Si moja.

301
00:24:56,994 --> 00:24:59,923
